page.title: 18SHOPS IN KEELBY
page.content: In Keelby there are six shops they are all very useful there is everything you could ask for. We have two super markets really. Tates is in the main shopping area and Spar is the other one. We have a bakery which sells fresh cakes,buns,fresh ham and other meats. It also sells free range eggs. The newsagents sells sweets tobaco and newspapers. It also sells groceries and toys.The offlicence sells wine, beer and other spirits.They have also got a wide choice of videos that you can borrow.We have a chip shop which is very useful.My family usually get fish and chips on Saturday.The only shop in the village that sells wool and other sewing materials is called the Wool Shop.
